metadata.description: Bad AI Happy Birthday Greetings: Animals shows off 400 weird, wild, and wacky 100% AI generated birthday greetings. We prompted, and the AI answered in all of its awkward glory -- thus we've deemed these "Bad AI.") This set of 400 cards on an ERC721A contract is sure to bring a smile. Issued at random and includes the animal in the metadata. Happy Birthday!
metadata.name: Bad AI Happy Birthday Greetings: Animals #1
